          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-1" n="1">Come, follow me by the smell, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-2" n="2">Here's delicate onions to sell,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-3" n="3">I promise to use you well.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-4" n="4">They make the blood warmer,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-5" n="5">You'll feed like a farmer:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-6" n="6">For this is every cook's opinion,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-7" n="7">No savoury dish without an onion;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-8" n="8">But lest your kissing should be spoiled,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-9" n="9">Your onions must be thoroughly boiled;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-10" n="10">Or else you may spare</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-11" n="11">Your mistress a share,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-12" n="12">The secret will never be known;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-13" n="13">She cannot discover</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-14" n="14">The breath of her lover</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-952BROGP-line-15" n="15">But think it as sweet as her own.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
